sql:
SELECT clip_name
FROM audio_clips
WHERE duration > 20.0;

SELECT clip_name
FROM audio_clips
WHERE duration > (SELECT AVG(duration) FROM audio_clips);

external_knowledge:
- High confidence score refers to a value above 0.8, indicating a high level of certainty in the calculated valence and arousal values; 
- Age range '26-35' is considered as a specific age group for this query, implying that 'groups' here refers to people within this age range; 
- Duration of more than 60 seconds is equivalent to more than 1 minute.

